 served as [[President of Iran]] from 1981 to 1989 until Khomeini's death.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/10/29/iran-irgc-islamic-revolutionary-guard-corps-kept-supreme-leader-ayatollah-ali-khamenei-power/ |title=Iran's IRGC Has Long Kept Khamenei in Power |first=Alex |last=Vatanka |date=29 October 2019 |access-date=4 January 2020 |work=[[Foreign Policy]]}}</ref>}}\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Iran|Politics}}\n*[[List of heads of state of Iran]]\n*[[Execution of Imam Khomeini's Order]]\n*[[Constitution of the Islamic Republic of Iran]]\n*[[Death and state funeral of Ruhollah Khomeini]]\n*[[1989 Iranian Supreme Leader election]]\n* [[Next Supreme Leader of Iran Election]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Supreme Leaders of Iran}}\n*[http://www.leader.ir Official website of the Office of the Supreme Leader]\n*[http://www.servat.unibe.ch/icl/ir00000_.html Iranian constitution]\n*[http://www.worldstatesmen.org/Iran.htm WorldStatesmen- Iran]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20110722055332/http://www.sssup.it/context_eng.jsp?ID_LINK=7945&area=47 Iran Electoral Archive - Supreme Leader]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-other|[[List of heads of state of Iran|Head of state of Iran]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[List of monarchs of Persia|Shah]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Supreme Leader|years=1979\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n{{s-end}}\n{{Iran topics}}\n{{Heads of state and government of Asia}}\n{{Ruhollah Khomeini}}\n{{Ali Khamenei}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of office-holders in Iran|Supreme Leader]]\n[[Category:Positions of authority]]\n[[Category:Religious leadership roles]]\n[[Category:Supreme Leaders of Iran| ]]\n[[Category:Lists of political office-holders in Iran|Supreme Leader]]\n[[Category:Political terminology of Iran]]\n[[Category:Theocrats]]\n[[Category:Politics of Iran]]\n[[Category:1979 establishments in Iran]]\n", "name_user": "76.99.117.175", "label": "vandal", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Supreme_Leader_of_Iran